       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. PAYROLL.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       COPY EMPREC.
       01 WS-TOTAL      PIC 9(7)V99 VALUE ZERO.
       01 WS-RATE       PIC 9(3)V99 VALUE 0.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       MAIN-PARA.
           PERFORM INIT-PARA.
           CALL 'TAXCALC' USING WS-TOTAL WS-RATE.
           PERFORM WRITE-PARA.
           STOP RUN.
       INIT-PARA.
           MOVE ZERO TO WS-TOTAL.
       WRITE-PARA.
           DISPLAY 'TOTAL: ' WS-TOTAL.
